## ğŸ§­ Routes

* `GET /`
  Fetches records via HubSpot CRM API
  `GET /crm/v3/objects/{OBJECT_TYPE}?properties=...&limit=100&archived=false`
  Renders `views/homepage.pug` â†’ an HTML table with columns for each property in `COBJ_PROPERTIES`.

* `GET /update-cobj`
  Renders `views/updates.pug`: an HTML form generated from `COBJ_PROPERTIES` (text inputs + textarea for long text). Includes a â€œReturn to the main pageâ€ link.

* `POST /update-cobj`
  Creates a new CRM record:
  `POST /crm/v3/objects/{OBJECT_TYPE}` with body:

  ```json
  { "properties": { "<prop1>": "...", "<prop2>": "..." } }
  ```

  On success redirects back to `/`.

