## ğŸ§ª Testing

1. Visit `http://localhost:3000/update-cobj`
2. Fill in the fields (at least those listed in `REQUIRED_PROPS`).
3. Submit â†’ youâ€™ll be redirected to `/` and see the new row in the table.

